Okeniyi (/ˈdaɪoʊ oʊˈkɛniiː/; a mụrụ na June 14, 1988) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na Naijiria na America, nke a maara nke ọma maka ịrụ ọrụ Thresh na The Hunger Games na Danny Dyson na Terminator Genisys

A mụrụ Dayo na Jos ma o tolite na Lagos, Nigeria, ma nwee ụmụnne anọ. Nna ya bụ onye ọrụ omenala lara ezumike nká si Nigeria, nne ya bụ onye nkuzi akwụkwọ si Kenya.
N'afọ 2003, ya na ezinụlọ ya kwagara Indiana, United States, site na Nigeria ma mesịa kwaga California. O nwetara nzere bachelọ na nkwukọrịta ọhụụ na Mahadum Anderson (Indiana) n'afọ 2009.

Tupu a tụnye ya na The Hunger Games, Okeniyi rụrụ ọrụ na ụlọ ihe nkiri obodo na obere ihe nkiri. Okeniyi pụtara n'afọ 2014 na ihe nkiri Endless Love, gosikwara Danny Dyson na ihe nkiri nke 2015 Terminator Genisys ma pụta ìhè na usoro NBC Shades of Blue
Okeniyi ga-apụta na ihe nkiri Fresh, nke a na-eme atụmatụ igosi n'afọ 2022 Sundance Film Festival.
